\pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f0\fs22 1r\endash 4v \plain \f0\scaps\fs22 Kalendarium\plain \f0\fs22 , fragmentarisch: Januar, Februar, M\u228 \'e4rz und Mai, nicht alle Tage besetzt; bemerkenswert: 7.1. \plain \f0\i\fs22 Luciani presbiteri\plain \f0\fs22 , 22.1. \u8250 \'9b\plain \f0\i\fs22 Vincentii mar\-tiris\plain \f0\fs22 \u8249 \'8b, 1.3. \plain \f0\i\fs22 David confessoris\plain \f0\fs22 , 4.3. \plain \f0\i\fs22 Adriani martiris\plain \f0\fs22 , 17.3. \plain \f0\i\fs22 Ghertrudis virginis\plain \f0\fs22 , 22.3. \plain \f0\i\fs22 Pauli episcopi\plain \f0\fs22 , 27.3. \plain \f0\i\fs22 Resurrectio domini\plain \f0\fs22 , 15.5. \plain \f0\i\fs22 Sancti Tymothei\plain \f0\fs22 , 18.5. \plain \f0\i\fs22 Marci pape\plain \f0\fs22 , 20.5. \plain \f0\i\fs22 Sabine virginis\plain \f0\fs22  (statt am 20.7.?).}

