\pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f0\fs22 94r\endash 100r \plain \f0\scaps\fs22 Gebete. \plain \f0\fs22 \u8250 \'9b\plain \f0\i\fs22 Oracio\plain \f0\fs22 .\u8249 \'8b\plain \f0\i\fs22  Precor te, piissime domine Ihesu Christe, propter illam caritatem qua tu rex celestis pendebas in cruce . . .\plain \f0\fs22  (95r) \u8250 \'9b\plain \f0\i\fs22 Oracio\plain \f0\fs22 .\u8249 \'8b \plain \f0\i\fs22 Deus qui voluisti pro redemptione mundi a Iudei\plain \f0\fs22 [s]\plain \f0\i\fs22  reprobari\plain \f0\fs22  ... (96v) \u8250 \'9b\plain \f0\i\fs22 Oracio\plain \f0\fs22 .\u8249 \'8b \plain \f0\i\fs22 Deus propicius esto michi peccatori et custos mei in omnibus diebus vite mee. Deus Abraham, deus Ysaac, deus Iacob miserere mei ...\plain \f0\fs22  (98r) \u8250 \'9b\plain \f0\i\fs22 De beata Susanna oracio.\u8249 \'8b Deus qui contra falsos testes beatum Danielem mittere voluisti et bea\-tam Susannam a periculis mortis liberasti ...\plain \f0\fs22  (98v) \u8250 \'9b\plain \f0\i\fs22 Oracio de beata Barbara virgine\plain \f0\fs22 .\u8249 \'8b \plain \f0\i\fs22 O beata Barbara deoque virgo electa, cui tota trinitas reuelata ...\plain \f0\fs22  (99r) \u8250 \'9b\plain \f0\i\fs22 Oracio\plain \f0\fs22 .\u8249 \'8b \plain \f0\i\fs22 Intercessio, quesumus domine, beate Barbare gloriose . . .\plain \f0\fs22  (99v) \u8250 \'9b\plain \f0\i\fs22 Salutacio ad Mariam Magdalenam\plain \f0\fs22 .\u8249 \'8b \plain \f0\i\fs22 Ave Maria Magdalena, apostolorum apo\-stola, dominus tecum, benedicta tu...\plain \f0\fs22  }

